s thoroughly\nthe background and open problems, and provide many examples and explanations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Aug 2014 10:00:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Aug 2014 15:20:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 16 Nov 2014 12:26:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 11 Apr 2016 18:39:27 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2017 21:06:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-24"}
